# Phase 157.B — apps/external/Kconfig template.
#
# NuttX's apps/Kconfig sources every apps/<category>/Kconfig at
# preconfig time. For external apps, NuttX expects a single
# apps/external/Kconfig that osource's each sub-app's Kconfig.
#
# Phase 157.C's staging script copies this file verbatim to
# `$NUTTX_APPS_DIR/external/Kconfig` so menuconfig surfaces the
# integration shell (NROS) + every example
# (NROS_EXAMPLE_<NAME>_<LANG>) under
# `Application Configuration > External Modules`.
#
# `osource` (lowercase-s) is NuttX kconfig's optional-source
# directive that silently no-ops if the path glob matches zero
# files — keeps the menuconfig run from erroring on a tree where
# only some examples were symlinked.

menu "External Modules"

osource "$APPSDIR/external/*/Kconfig"

endmenu
